          "source_html": "<div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><strong>Questions 27 – 31</strong><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Choose <strong>YES </strong>if the statement agrees with the claims of the writer, choose <strong>NO </strong>if the statement contradicts the claims of the writer, or choose <strong>NOT GIVEN </strong>if it is impossible to say what the writer thinks about this.</p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">27</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><strong>The Pacific islands were uninhabited when migrants arrived by sea from Southeast Asia.</strong></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. YES</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p>uninhabited，Southeast Asia</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">A段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">The many tiny islands of the Pacific Ocean had no human population until ancestors of today&#39;s islanders sailed from Southeast Asia in ocean-going canoes approximately 2,000 years ago. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到在人们从东南亚来到这里之前，许多太平洋的小岛是无人居住的。原文中“<span style=\"font-family: Arial; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">The many tiny islands of the Pacific Ocean...<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">”</span></span>并不是想表达“太平洋上的部分岛屿”，而是想强调岛屿数量众多。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">同义替换：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">no human population</span>=<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">uninhabited</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">ancestors of today&#39;s islanders</span>=migrants</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">28</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Andrew Sharp was the first person to write about the migrants to islanders.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. NO</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Andrew Sharp</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">A段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Although the romantic vision of some early twentieth-century writers of fleets of heroic navigators simultaneously setting sail had come to be considered by later investigators to be exaggerated, no considered assessment of Pacific voyaging was forthcoming until 1956 when the American historian Andrew Sharp published his research.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到安德鲁·夏普在1956年发表了他的研究，但并不是说他是第一个研究这个主题的。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">29</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Andrew Sharp believed migratory voyages were based on more on luck than skill.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. YES</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">good fortune</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Sharp challenged the &#39;heroic vision&#39; by asserting that the expertise of the navigators was limited, and that the settlement of the islands was not systematic, being more dependent on good fortune by drifting canoes. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到夏普认定居为更多的依赖于运气。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">同义替换：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">luck=</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">good fortune</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">dependent on</span>=base on</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">30</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Despite being controversial, Andrew Sharp&#39;s research had positive results.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. YES</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">controversia</span>l，<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">positive results</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Sharp&#39;s theory was widely challenged, and deservedly so. If nothing else, however, it did spark renewed interest in the topic and precipitated valuable new research.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到夏普的理论受到了广泛的质疑，但它确实重新激起了人们对这个话题的兴趣，并促成了有价值的新研究，说明它产生了积极的作用。</span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">同义替换：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">controversia</span>l=challenged</p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">positive results</span>=<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">valuable new research</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">31</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Edwin Doran disagreed with the findings of Lewis&#39;s research.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> C. NOT GIVEN</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Edwin Doran</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">E</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">The geographer Edwin Doran followed a quite different approach. He was interested in obtaining exact data on canoe sailing performance, and to that end employed the latest electronic instrumentation. Doran traveled on board traditional sailing canoes in some of the most remote parts of the Pacific, all the while using his instruments to record canoe speeds in different wind strengths – from gales to calms – the angle canoes could sail relative to the wind. In the process, he provided the first really precise attributes of traditional sailing canoes.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">原文提到Edwin Doran采用了一种完全不同的方法，并<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">没有提到</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Edwin Dora</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">不同意</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">David Lewi</span>s<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">的观点。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><strong>Questions 32 – 36</strong><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Choose the correct answer.</p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">32</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>David Lewis&#39;s research was different because</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> he observed traditional navigators at work.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> he conducted test voyages using his own yacht.\r\n\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> he carried no modern instruments on test voyages.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> he spoke the same language as the islanders he sailed with.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. he observed traditional navigators at work.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">David Lewis&#39;s research</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">D</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">In 1965, David Lewis, a physician and experienced yachtsman, set to work using his own unique philosophy: he took the yacht he had owned for many years and navigated through the islands in order to contact those men who still find their way at sea using traditional methods. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">David Lewis</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">带领传统的航海家在他们的独木舟上进行了试航</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">33</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>What did David Lewis&#39;s research discover about traditional navigators?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> They used the sun and moon to find their position.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> They could not sail further than about 1,000 nautical miles.\r\n\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> They knew which direction they were sailing in.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> They were able to drift for long distances.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> C. They knew which direction they were sailing in.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">traditional navigators</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">D</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Far from drifting, as proposed by Sharp, Lewis found that ancient navigators would have known which course to steer by memorizing which stars rose and set in certain positions along the horizon and this gave them fixed directions by which to steer their boats.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">David Lewis</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">的研究表明，传统的航海家通过记忆星星来知道航行的方向。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">同义替换：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">traditional</span>=<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">ancient</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">34</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>What are we told about Edwin Doran&#39;s research?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> Data were collected after the canoes had returned to land.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> Canoe characteristics were recorded using modern instruments.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> Research was conducted in the most densely populated regions.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> Navigators were not allowed to see the instruments Doran used.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. Canoe characteristics were recorded using modern instruments.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Edwin Doran&#39;s research</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">E</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Doran traveled on board traditional sailing canoes in some of the most remote parts of the Pacific, all the while using his instruments to record canoe speeds in different wind strengths – from gales to calms – the angle canoes could sail relative to the wind.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Edwin Doran</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">在独木舟上使用现代仪器记录航行表现。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">35</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>Which of the following did Steven Horvath discover during his research?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_35\" id=\"opt_35_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q35\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_35_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> Canoe design was less important than human strength.\r\n\r\n\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_35\" id=\"opt_35_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q35\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_35_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> New research methods had to be developed for use in canoes.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_35\" id=\"opt_35_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q35\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_35_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> Navigators became very tired on the longest voyages.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_35\" id=\"opt_35_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q35\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_35_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> Human energy may have been used to assist sailing canoes.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> D. Human energy may have been used to assist sailing canoes.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Steven Horvath </span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">F</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Horvath was able to calculate the energy expenditure required to paddle canoes of this sort at times when there was no wind to fill the sails, or when the wind was contrary. He concluded that paddles, or perhaps long oars, could indeed have propelled for long distances what were primarily sailing vessels.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Horvath</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">能够计算出在没有风或逆风的情况下划动这种独木舟所需的能量消耗。他得出的结论是，桨确实可以推动主要是帆船的船只进行长距离航行，说明人的能量可以用来辅独木舟。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">36</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>What is the writer&#39;s opinion of P Wall Garrard&#39;s research?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_36\" id=\"opt_36_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q36\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_36_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> He is disappointed it was conducted in the laboratory.\r\n\r\n\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_36\" id=\"opt_36_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q36\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_36_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> He is impressed by the originality of the techniques used.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_36\" id=\"opt_36_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q36\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_36_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> He is surprised it was used to help linguists with their research.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_36\" id=\"opt_36_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q36\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_36_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> He is concerned that the islands studied are long distances apart.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. He is impressed by the originality of the techniques used.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">P Wall Garrard</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">G</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">段，“</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Clever adaptation of computer simulation techniques pioneered in other disciplines allowed him to produce convincing models suggesting the migrations were indeed systematic, but not simultaneous.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">”</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">原文提到他巧妙地运用了在其他学科中率先出现的计算机模拟技术，得出了令人信服的模型，说明</span>作<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">者对沃尔·加拉德的计算机模拟技术的独创性印象深刻。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">同义替换：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">convincing</span>=<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">impressed</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p><strong>Questions 37 – 40</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Complete each sentence with the correct ending. Choose the correct ending and move it into the gap.</p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"word-bank-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"wb-title\">Options (Word Bank):</div>\r\n        <div class=\"wb-grid\">\r\n            <div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>A.</strong> was the variety of experimental techniques used.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>B.</strong> was not of interest to young islanders today.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>C.</strong> was not conclusive evidence in support of a single theory.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>D.</strong> was being able to change their practices when necessary.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>E.</strong> was the first time humans intentionally crossed an ocean.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>F.</strong> was the speed with which it was conducted.</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"matrix-container\">\r\n        <table>\r\n            <thead><tr><th class=\"corner-header\">Question / Paragraph</th><th>A</th><th>B</th><th>C</th><th>D</th><th>E</th><th>F</th></tr></thead>\r\n            <tbody>\r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">37</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">One limitation in the information produced by all of this research is that it <span class=\"input-blank\">________</span></span></p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_37\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_37\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_37\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_37\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_37\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_37\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：C</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>limitation，research</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>H段，“Quite correctly, none of the researchers tried to use their findings to prove one theory or another; experiments such as these cannot categorically confirm or negate a hypothesis.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到没有一个研究人员试图用他们的发现来证明一个或另一个理论;像这样的实验不能绝对地证实或否定一个假设。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">38</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">The best thing about this type of research <span class=\"input-blank\">________</span></span></p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_38\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_38\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_38\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_38\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_38\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_38\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：A</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>The best thing</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>H段，“The strength of this research lay in the range of methodologies employed.When we splice together these findings, we can propose that traditional navigators used a variety of canoe types, sources of water and navigation techniques, and it was this adaptability which was their greatest accomplishment. ”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提出所使用的不同研究方法的重要性，强调不同方法的结合提供了对太平洋航行实践的更全面的了解。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：</p><p>best=strength</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">39</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">The most important achievement of traditional navigators <span class=\"input-blank\">________</span></span></p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_39\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_39\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_39\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_39\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_39\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_39\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：D</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>achievement，traditional navigators</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>H段，“When we splice together these findings, we can propose that traditional navigators used a variety of canoe types, sources of water and navigation techniques, and it was this adaptability which was their greatest accomplishment. ”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提出适应他们的技术是他们最大的成就。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：</p><p>greatest=the most important&nbsp;</p><p>accomplishment=achievement</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr class=\"q-row\">\r\n            <td class=\"q-text-cell\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-q-wrapper\">\r\n                    <span class=\"matrix-num\">40</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"matrix-content\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">The migration of people from Asia to the Pacific <span class=\"input-blank\">________</span></span></p></div>\r\n                    <button class=\"mini-btn\">🔍</button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_40\" value=\"A\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_40\" value=\"B\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_40\" value=\"C\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_40\" value=\"D\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_40\" value=\"E\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\"></td><td class=\"radio-cell\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q_matrix_53654_40\" value=\"F\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\"ans-row-hidden\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">\r\n                <div class=\"matrix-analysis\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-key\">✅ 正确答案：E</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-body\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>migration，Pacific</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>H段，“Furthermore, the canoes of the navigators were not drifting helplessly at sea but were most likely part of a systematic migration; as such, the Pacific peoples were able to view the ocean as an avenue, not a barrier, to communication before any other race on Earth.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提出提到太平洋的岛民视海洋为交通途径，这表明他们在人类历史上是第一个有意识地跨越大洋的群体。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </div>",
